text: Mihri is a word of Turkish language origin, and it may refer to: *Mihri Pektaş (1895–1979), Turkish school teacher and one of the first 18 female parliament members of Turkey *Mihri Belli (1915–2011),Turkish socialist politician *Mihri Hatun (died 1506), Ottoman female poet *Mihri Müşfik Hanım (1886–c. 1954), Turkish female painter *Sude Mihri Çınar (born 1995), Turkish women's footballer Category:Turkish given names
title: Mihri
